{"tid":2018763,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日第一日返IT 好想喊","createTime":"2020-05-15T21:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T11:40:08.000Z","uid":57864,"like":16,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"684140da3ebd21a741450e605c56dc2edf15d0d7","tid":2018763,"uid":57864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:31:54.000Z","msg":"之前從來未過揼過code，第一轉就要揼8行C++，頂硬上，係就係慢小小，去完一轉，手已經好硬，第二轉揼8行已經手軟，行唔到咁，師兄睇量我，俾我6行先，勉強頂到，好不容易先捱到中午飯，去左科學園一間茶餐廳到食，咁送左例湯黎， 攞起隻匙羹，我屌，提唔能起，右手已經硬能曬，我要用個頭壓低黎飲湯，心諗，仆街喇，重有半日點捱，好，食完飯，又推過，又熱又曬，已經出到沒曬汗，我知再唔飲水，一定會死，我愉雞經過7-11買支野飲，一野飲曬都唔夠，但起碼有返汗出，到岩岩放工時，佢地問我返唔返第二日，我話唔返，第日就辭職，好敬佩佢地，份工真係唔簡單。"},{"pid":"e10f20c2ccf9401925363f8338a4df01293c2feb","tid":2018763,"uid":228317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb87ee3f4e0809eb5f0831a20141523ec4cef6fe","tid":2018763,"uid":44884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:47:21.000Z","msg":"得喇"},{"pid":"6ef78d8677f043a7e6804bac6bdd6a97344c2b90","tid":2018763,"uid":97828,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:13:00.000Z","msg":"要明咗d existing code , 先可以build上去"},{"pid":"6e3b16c043010339ed64a6a80d139345441dda91","tid":2018763,"uid":22974,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:14:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a03145307ed3429196300068384be6c34bd9030","tid":2018763,"uid":97828,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:14:32.000Z","msg":"寫code都係抄人再改少少就成為自己d code"},{"pid":"efa4512c7a3a07a9f0f9832385066300e7a30127","tid":2018763,"uid":213607,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:28:40.000Z","msg":"上左十幾年登呢個真心未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1d7f55ab83c6e994f90fe2aec1d08e08f82853","tid":2018763,"uid":65162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22: